_text = "As if someone grabbed my arm, I was pulled back into reality. I was standing in this cave once again.I still couldn't remember who I was, but I felt a flicker of hope as I proceed forward.\n\nAs I continued further into the cave, I begin to hear faint sounds. It's almost as if I can hear the crackling of a campfire or snow crunching under car tires.\n\nHowever, they seem to be coming from opposite directions once again.\n\nDo I explore the campground on the left or investigate the snowy landscape on the right? "

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, Monitor, MonitorNo, MonitorYes, PropaneFireMemory, FieldMemory, false)
